titleStmt.title: The Earl of Warwicks surrender of the ordinance and authoritie formerly granted by both Houses of Parliament, for his being Lord High Admirall of England, &c. Presented in the House of Peeres 10. April 1645. and communicated from their Lordships to the House of Commons at a conference held the same day. Printed and published according to order.
